    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">1: General Menus and Toolbars</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><image src="1r.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> Menu bar</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><image src="MD-MenuBar-main.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="0,0,38,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Menu-File"><title>File menu drop-down</title></area><area shape="rect" coords="41,0,79,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/><area shape="rect" coords="82,0,120,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Add"/><area shape="rect" coords="123,0,161,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="169,0,207,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Filters"/><area shape="rect" coords="219,0,257,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-View"/><area shape="rect" coords="266,0,304,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Help"/><area shape="rect" coords="398,0,542,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Release-Version-Build"/></imagemap></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The menus - <text styleclass="T_Menu">File, Edit, Filters, View, Help -</text> have commands that are common to most CAD applications.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Add" styleclass="T_Menu">Add menu</link> has the commands to build your models.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">General toolbars</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbars</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">above</text> and <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There is an icon to <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">expand and collapse</text> each <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbar.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbars</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">collapsed</text> when you start <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">General toolbars <text style="color:#ff0000;">ABOVE</text> graphic-area</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-Menu-Maintop.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="150,2,190,78" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="97,77,191,95" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="202,2,243,98" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="107,96,244,115" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="260,2,300,116" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="122,116,299,135" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="311,3,351,138" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="132,138,351,157" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="363,2,403,157" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="142,157,404,176" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="417,3,457,180" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/><area shape="rect" coords="152,177,458,195" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/></imagemap></image></para>
